title: Simply Perfect Party Cakes for Kids [PDF] [StormRG]
description:
Simply Perfect Party Cakes for Kids: Easy Step-by-Step Novelty Cakes for Children's Parties
Author: Zoe Clark
Published: 2014
Publisher: David & Charles
ISBN: 9781446304266
Format: Retail PDF


Simply Perfect Party Cakes for Kids is a stunning collection of 12 easy-to-achieve novelty cakes for children from internationally renowned cake decorator Zoe Clark. The easy-to-follow step-by-step photography will show you in detail how to create and build up each of the cake designs and with Zoe's tried and tested cake recipes, you'll soon be making amazing party cakes at home that you will be proud to show off!

The cake designs include a baby elephant design, a 3D toy box cake, an enchanted garden design and a circus-inspired cake for younger children as well as a surfing cake, paintball cake and make-up cake for older children.

Zoe runs her own cake business just outside London, UK. She also runs regular cake decorating classes and has over 35,000 online followers
